      <title>由于公用事业公司寻求交易，波士顿附近的液化天然气工厂可能会避免关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/lng-plant-near-boston-may-avoid-closure-as-utilities-seek-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿附近一个面临关闭风险的重要液化天然气进口码头可能会获得新的生命，因为两家地区公用事业公司正在寻求从该设施采购燃料的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/lng-plant-near-boston-may-avoid-closure-as-utilities-seek-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 18:10:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
